{"tid":2184493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔣麗芸：如果喺全民檢測驗到陽性，係好事嚟","createTime":"2020-09-01T14:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T11:35:41.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b74681f546fbadff78d67ca00957496c2c436831","tid":2184493,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"首次接受病毒檢測的民建聯蔣麗芸指心情並不緊張，又雀躍稱「對啲未試過嘅嚠，緊係覺得好好奇！」蔣表示「做完緊係安心啲」，又指完成檢測後「對未來自己嘅防疫會仲小心」。她指結果「做完係陽性嘅，係好事喎就仲好，咁就救咗你自己一命同埋身邊嘅家人。」蔣麗芸又大讚是日立法會的安排，覺得「環境好好」。被問及會否持續接受病毒測試，她則稱在「健康碼」實施後會再作檢測。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯葛珮帆則在檢測過程中，刻意把屏風內的椅子靠前，讓記者拍攝其檢測過程，並全程微笑，在完成檢測後更雙手舉起「V字」勝利手勢...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077014&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=f5aad3c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077014&h=99b6a94e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077014</a>"},{"pid":"3f02ed5592ce7d85f909de37842a75ea66edae16","tid":2184493,"uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"400eb084c1764430026ad9122cc4c5322e87b08a","tid":2184493,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"6f8690e52daaabd5096dbb78970dbadccea43ffd","tid":2184493,"uid":47697,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢測到陽性，係好事嚟"},{"pid":"39de56f0d6b287ec88c1ed50ef364f42f9aa222a","tid":2184493,"uid":31200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"陰陽不分 果然同指鹿為馬係fd"},{"pid":"833e7d8645a7894c0683fdc073f755faedcafdb2","tid":2184493,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXNSoCB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c